                                <h1 class="f--secondary f--uppercase">Our Mission</h1>
                                <div class="f--desc"><p>The National WWII Museum tells the story of the American experience in&nbsp;<em>the war that changed the world</em>—why it was fought, how it was won, and what it means today—so that all generations will understand the price of freedom and be inspired by what they learn.</p></div>
