                    <h3 class="f--title f--tertiary"><a href="/war/articles/lost-wwii-shipwrecks-discovered-aleutian-waters-attu-island" rel="bookmark" target="_self">New Underwater Exploration of Attu’s World War II Shipwrecks</a></h3>
            
    

    
          <div class="f--desc">
        <p>A multinational team has rediscovered long-lost WWII shipwrecks off Attu Island in Alaska, using sonar, drones, and archival research to document a forgotten underwater battlefield.</p>
