                    <h3 class="f--title f--tertiary"><a href="/about-us/notes-museum/meet-author-robin-judd-between-two-worlds" rel="bookmark" target="_self">Meet the Author: Robin Judd, "Between Two Worlds"</a></h3>
            
    

    
          <div class="f--desc">
        <p>Facing the harrowing task of rebuilding a life in the wake of the Holocaust, many Jewish survivors, community and religious leaders, and Allied soldiers viewed marriage between Jewish women and military personnel as a way to move forward after unspeakable loss.</p>
