                    <h3 class="f--title f--tertiary"><a href="/about-us/notes-museum/meet-author-james-b-conroy-devils-will-get-no-rest" rel="bookmark" target="_self">Meet the Author: James B. Conroy, 'The Devils Will Get No Rest'</a></h3>
            
    

    
